Preheat the oven to 160C/350F/Gas 4.Combine all the dry ingredients in a bowl, add the egg yolk and vanilla and mix well to form a dough.Lightly knead the dough on a floured work surface until smooth then shape into a log and place on a baking tray lined with parchment.Bake for 25 minutes, allow to cool, then cut into slices about 1cm/Â½in thick.  Place slices onto the baking tray and bake again for 5-10 minutes.